OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be a
OL,6,Fbright evening in the east but
OL,7,Fcloudier in the west with showers or
OL,8,Flonger spells of rain. The showers
OL,9,Fwill spread eastwards overnight.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTuesday:FA largely cloudy day with
OL,12,Fbright intervals and showers. Some of
OL,13,Fthese could be heavy and thundery.
OL,14,
OL,15,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,16,FSunshine and heavy showers on
OL,17,FWednesday. A dry and sunny start to
OL,18,FThursday but cloud and patchy rain
OL,19,Fspreading east. Sunshine and showers
OL,20,Flikely on Friday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
